  "title": "sales executive",
  "description": "<p>Job description:</p><p></p><p>We are looking for a motivated and results-driven Sales Executive to join our growing team. The ideal candidate will be responsible for developing new business opportunities, maintaining client relationships, and achieving sales targets.</p><p></p><p>Key Responsibilities:</p><p>•⁠  ⁠Develop and generate new sales leads</p><p>•⁠  ⁠Maintain and grow relationships with existing clients</p><p>•⁠  ⁠Prepare quotations, follow up on sales enquiries, and close deals</p><p>•⁠  ⁠Coordinate with internal teams to ensure smooth project execution</p><p>•⁠  ⁠Achieve monthly and quarterly sales targets</p><p>•⁠  ⁠Attend meetings and presentations with clients when required</p><p>Requirement:</p><p>•⁠  ⁠Minimum 3 years of relevant sales experience</p><p>•⁠  ⁠Chinese-speaking candidates preferred (to liaise with Chinese-speaking clients)</p><p>•⁠  ⁠Proficient in English and Chinese (spoken and written)</p><p>•⁠  ⁠Strong communication and negotiation skills</p><p>•⁠  ⁠Self-motivated, independent, and target-oriented</p><p>•⁠  ⁠Experience in related industry is an advantage</p><p>What we offer:</p><p>•⁠  ⁠Competitive salary + commission</p><p>•⁠  ⁠Career growth opportunities</p><p>•⁠  ⁠Supportive and dynamic working environment</p><p>•⁠  ⁠Working location near MRT</p>",
